---
// Performance.astro - Sección analítica de motor y eficiencia
---

<section id="performance" class="py-24 bg-[#F8F9FA]">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#DA291C] border border-[#DA291C]/30 bg-[#DA291C]/5">
          Motorización Avanzada
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(2.25rem,4vw,3.5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold text-[#3B3938] mb-6">
          Rendimiento<br/>
          <span class="text-[#646464] font-normal">Sin Precedentes.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg">
          La nueva motorización BlueHDi combina una eficiencia térmica superior con una respuesta ágil. Diseñada específicamente para resistir las exigencias del transporte urbano e interurbano continuo.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-10">
          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-[#DA291C]/20 border-l-[#DA291C]">
            <div class="text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-[#3B3938] leading-none mb-2">100<span class="text-[1.25rem] text-[#646464] font-normal"> CV</span></div>
            <p class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-[#646464]">Potencia Máxima</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-l-[#DA291C]">
            <div class="text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-[#3B3938] leading-none mb-2">254<span class="text-[1.25rem] text-[#646464] font-normal"> Nm</span></div>
            <p class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-[#646464]">Torque Eficiente</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-l-[#DA291C]">
            <div class="text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-[#3B3938] leading-none mb-2">5.1<span class="text-[1.25rem] text-[#646464] font-normal"> L/100</span></div>
            <p class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-[#646464]">Consumo Mixto</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-l-[#DA291C]">
            <div class="text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-[#3B3938] leading-none mb-2">6 MT<span class="text-[1.25rem] text-[#646464] font-normal"></span></div>
            <p class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-[#646464]">Caja Manual</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Graphic/Image -->
      <div class="relative w-full aspect-square lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full min-h-[400px]">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#E0E5E9] rounded-lg overflow-hidden transform lg:translate-x-8 lg:translate-y-8"></div>
        <img 
          src="/citroen-berlingo/images/gallery-exterior.png" 
          alt="Desempeño aerodinámico Citroën" 
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl relative z-10"
        />
        
        <!-- Floating badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-6 shadow-xl rounded-lg z-20 w-64 border border-[#E7E7E7]/50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#DA291C]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#DA291C]">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[14px] font-bold text-[#3B3938] uppercase tracking-[0.05em]">Start & Stop</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[13px] text-[#646464] leading-relaxed">Sistema inteligente que apaga el motor en semáforos, ahorrando un 10% adicional de combustible urbano.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
